{"tid":1012571,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"定價 $4,380！Google Pixel 3 Lite 未上市已被負評","createTime":"2019-02-07T16:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T18:28:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f4bf895276e925da85a1b0788eba4c0d3d821c","tid":1012571,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"昨日分享過 Amazon 美國網站增加繁中介面，方便網友可以去掃貨，其中一件可以透過 Amazon 入手的就食 Google Pixel 3 和 Pixel 3 XL，至今 Pixel 都未曾在香港推出行貨。有消息指 Google 將會在短期內發表新的 Pixel ，不過並非 Pixel 4，而是傳聞已久的 Pixel 3 Lite 和 Pixel 3 XL Lite。<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-02/07/212333/uniqlo_1_ec3c1be7e8d76989fa2054319cf92c2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-02%2F07%2F212333%2Funiqlo_1_ec3c1be7e8d76989fa2054319cf92c2d.jpg&h=66af4c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外國網站 MSP 表示，兩款型號 G020B 和 G020F 已經釋出，而且亦安排由 Foxconn 代工生產，至於是中國還是印度的廠房暫時未能確定。雖然實際上市日期還未公開，不過 Pixel 3 Lite 據說已經在印度有了定價，售價將會在 40,000 印度盧比以下（折合 HK$4,380），有別於 Pixel 3 屬高階旗艦，Lite 型號定位為中階機，這個定價被網民大罵不值，認為使用原生系統的 Nokia 或走高性價比路線的 OnePlus 更加可取。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4541/212333/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4541%2F212333%2F1%2F&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2Bcm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=9bad74a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4541/212333/1/</a>"},{"pid":"3baacf425b507a0d22f94f959666c55bfc17da7f","tid":1012571,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:29:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97bb9053ce904800e6dc104737f073f157c3a8b0","tid":1012571,"uid":128600,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"又冇行又要貴....."},{"pid":"000da39eb34e4b2b5c9713b5c6c916ec27a3ec2c","tid":1012571,"uid":65780,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:38